title: Sabores Dominican Restaurant
typeOfFood: Ovo, Take-out, Caribbean, Catering, Dominican, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Dominican restaurant with vegan options highlighted on a chalkboard in the front. Vegans could get the Dominican spaghetti, meatless eggplant balls, rice with pigeon peas, rice with either pinto or black beans, lentil soup. Often runs out of dishes, so calling ahead can be helpful.
